OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChancellor set to tighten  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FUniversal Credit rules     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thousands more part time workers could 
OL,6, have their benefits reduced if they do 
OL,7, not take "active steps" to work more,  
OL,8, under a planned welfare reform.        
OL,10,FChancellor Kwasi Kwarteng is expected  
OL,11,Fto announce a shake-up of the benefits 
OL,12,Fsystem to "get Britain working again". 
OL,14,FPart of the plan targets Universal     
OL,15,FCredit claimants working up to 15 hours
OL,16,Fa week at the National Living Wage.    
OL,18,FLabour's Jonathan Ashworth said the    
OL,19,Fplan threatened those on low pay with  
OL,20,Fsanctions for not working hard enough. 
